Viva Questions

What is Apache?

Apache is an open-source web server used to host websites.

What is Port 80?

Port 80 is the default HTTP port.

What is Port 22?

Port 22 is used for SSH remote login.

Where is the default Apache webpage stored?

/var/www/html/index.html

Command to start Apache?

sudo systemctl start apache2

Command to check Apache status?

sudo systemctl status apache2

